title: Risen League of Legends Team Returning to the Scene: Looking for Players D4+

embed.description: Risen is seeking members who aspire for glory in the eSports world and want to rise up to the challenge. We will be seeking players from Diamond 4+, however exceptions may apply if we see you are above your current skill level and have something to bring to the organisation.

body:
Risen is slowly opening it's doors to the League of Legends eSports scene once again, looking to return to our short lived glory days. We are seeking to reform our organisation, and allowing League of Legends to lead the charge in providing a new image as a whole. If you are looking to join a team, Risen will be recruiting players of Diamond 4+. See you on the other side!
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScASMVv-Y-FtEjxKaCxtrgZEGPQhoS06Gnx_69GhIeMcrvqyw/viewform

If you would prefer, you can forward your interests to me at rilez ライリー#7323.
